                  <li>Yeah, there is maybe some truth in it.</li>
                  <li>Nah</li>
                  <li>TIL</li>
                  <button type='button' class="add-answer-button add-default educational-default" id="green-button">Use this Default</button>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li><a href="#">Sports</a>
                <ul>
                  <li>Amazing skills</li>
